<TEXT>
ITC Classic Finance, the Indian financial services group, is seeking a
partnership with Threadneedle Asset Management, a BAT subsidiary, in order
to promote an asset management company in India.
Mr Feroze Vevaina, an ITC Classic director, said the two companies had
